
### Create a report
POST http://localhost:3000/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "make": "toyota",
  "model": "corolla",
  "year": 1980,
  "millage": 150000,
  "lng": 0,
  "lat": 0,
  "price": 20000
}


### Change approval

PATCH http://localhost:3000/reports/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true
}